original_title: De Vliegende Panters: Ebbinge, Vrijdag en De Bekker
overview: Stage registration of the fourth comedy special (2006-2008) by the Dutch comedy troupe De Vliegende Panters (The Flying Panters). This show tells the story about who the Vliegende Panters really are.
tagline: The Panters are still going strong
title: De Vliegende Panters: Ebbinge, Vrijdag en De Bekker
